  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a6a0ebe69b3164f6e91f94a88da27730, type: 3}
  m_Name: Chief Prologue Dialogue 3
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  Lines:
  - charName: Chief Vandham
    line: Now that you two are here, I have a favor to ask from both of you.
    reaction: 
    choices: []
    redirectDialogueIndex: -1
  - charName: Fiona
    line: Oh! A special request from the chief?
    reaction: 
    choices: []
    redirectDialogueIndex: -1
  - charName: Chief Vandham
    line: Wild slimes have been growing quite restless in the nearby forest.
    reaction: 
    choices: []
    redirectDialogueIndex: -1
  - charName: Chief Vandham
    line: With how many roaming around the area, it'll threaten the very safety of
      our village.
    reaction: 
    choices: []
    redirectDialogueIndex: -1
  - charName: Chief Vandham
    line: I want you two to work together to take them out.
    reaction: 
    choices: []
    redirectDialogueIndex: -1
  - charName: Fiona
    line: Really chief? Are you sure? But why choose us?
    reaction: 
    choices: []
    redirectDialogueIndex: -1
  - charName: Chief Vandham
    line: You two have shown me your strength in the way you fight. I see potential
      in both of you.
    reaction: 
    choices: []
    redirectDialogueIndex: -1
  - charName: Chief Vandham
    line: Thus, I shall assign this task to you both. I trust that you two will succeed.
    reaction: 
    choices: []
    redirectDialogueIndex: -1
  - charName: Chief Vandham
    line: Report back to me when you have finished. May the gods keep you well.
    reaction: 
    choices: []
    redirectDialogueIndex: -1
